JetBrains Mono NL (no-ligatures), v2.304
  Copyright 2020 The JetBrains Mono Project Authors
  Licensed under the SIL Open Font License, Version 1.1
  Upstream: https://github.com/JetBrains/JetBrainsMono
  License text: src/main/assets/fonts/OFL.txt

The NL ("no-ligatures") variants are bundled instead of the standard
JetBrains Mono so the cell-grid renderer is never tempted to substitute
a multi-cell ligature glyph for sequences like `==`, `=>`, `!=`, etc.
Even with `setFontFeatureSettings("liga 0")` set on the Paint, the NL
families guarantee no ligature substitution can happen at any layer
above us.
